name: Rym
tagline: A game about beauty, explosions, lines, squares and a triangle
body:
rym === A game about beauty, explosions, lines, squares and a triangle Download for [windows](https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/18120938/rym.exe) or build it for your self on linux: `cd (en mapp där du vill lägga det)`
`git clone git@github.com:mls-m5/rym.git`
`sudo apt-get install build-essential libsdl1.2-dev`
`cd rym`
`make`
`./rym`
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
